{
    "abstract": "The goal of this paper is to simulate the voters\u2019 behaviour given a voting method. Our approach uses a multi-agent simulation in order to model a voting process through many iterations, so that the voters can vote by taking into account the results of polls. Here we only tried basic rules and a single voting method, but further attempts could explore new features.",
